##UNDERSTANDING NICHE 
1- Working in a niche help people know about your channel in a much better way 
2- Not every niche income is same it mainly depends on the two factors CPM and RPM 
   CPM: Yotube earning for showing ads every time 
   RPM: Usually google keeps 45 percent of it and rest 55 percent is given which is called RPM 

NOTE - Financial channel earning is more beacuse they can earn more and spends more on CPM that does not make other niche channel earning small 

##FINDING NICHE 
1- Find a niche that suits your passion or otherwise you will get bored and frustrated after sometimes. 
2- If you have multiple passion then narrow down by looking at the market 
   If market is available in the niche then analyse the market , check the demand of the audience on other channel
and create content on it .
3- If market is not available then look at similar market and try to blend and create a new market which also maintain uniqueness 

NOTE - WHILE CHECKING OTHER CHANNEL LOOK AT THE PEOPLE WHAT KIND OF NEW THING THEY ARE 
DEMANDING AND IS THERE ANY NICHE THAT CAN BE CREATED OR NOT 

